PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Ethereum Transaction Monitoring App
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app allows you to monitor the Ethereum blockchain in real-time and get notified of new transactions as they occur. This is useful for applications that need to react quickly to on-chain events.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We run Ethereum nodes that connect directly to the blockchain network. Our app listens for new blocks and transactions, filters and processes the data, and sends notifications based on your configured rules.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kinds of notifications can I receive?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You can configure notifications for specific wallet addresses, smart contract events, transaction values above a certain threshold, and more. Notifications can be sent via webhooks, email, mobile push, or integrated into your own apps.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is this service free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We offer a free tier for small projects and startups. Paid tiers provide higher rate limits, more notification channels, dedicated support, and service guarantees for production environments.
